      • bindPosServer

        public static void bindPosServer(android.content.Context context)
        Bind to the POS service. This method must be called before any other functional methods. Note that if this method is called in a UI event handler method, it won't succeed until the event handler method returns. This method does not have a callback function, but the caller must still wait for the binding operation to succeed before calling any other method. This method will send a broadcast after the binding operation is successful. The ID of the broadcast is "com.ftpos.library.smartpos.binding.success" or "com.ftpos.library.smartpos.binding.fail".
        Parameters:
        context - context

      • bindPosServer

        public static void bindPosServer(android.content.Context context,
                                 OnServiceConnectCallback onServiceConnectCallback)
        Bind to the POS service. This method must be called before any other functional methods. Note that if this method is called in a UI event handler method, it won't succeed until the event handler method returns. The caller must wait for the binding operation to succeed before calling any other method. The callback method will be called after the binding operation. This method will send a broadcast after the binding operation is successful. The ID of the broadcast is "com.ftpos.library.smartpos.binding.success" or "com.ftpos.library.smartpos.binding.fail".
        Parameters:
        context - context
        onServiceConnectCallback - Return connection status.
